(43, 'RAM & Memory', 'Which of the following best describes ECC RAM?', 'Faster than standard RAM', 'Error-Correcting Code RAM that detects and corrects single-bit memory errors — used in servers', 'A type of video RAM', 'ROM that is erasable', 1, 'hard', '2026-05-23 16:25:36'),
(44, 'RAM & Memory', 'Running a 32-bit operating system limits usable RAM to approximately:', '128 GB', '16 GB', '4 GB', '64 GB', 2, 'medium', '2026-05-23 16:25:36'),
(45, 'RAM & Memory', 'SODIMM RAM modules are typically used in:', 'Desktop workstations', 'Laptops and compact systems', 'Server racks', 'Network switches', 1, 'easy', '2026-05-23 16:25:36'),
(46, 'Storage & RAID', 'What does RAID stand for?', 'Redundant Array of Independent Disks', 'Random Access Integrated Drive', 'Rapid Array of Internal Data', 'Read And Integrate Disk', 0, 'easy', '2026-05-23 16:25:36'),
(47, 'Storage & RAID', 'RAID 0 (striping) provides:', 'Data redundancy with backup', 'Increased read/write speed but NO fault tolerance — losing one disk loses all data', 'Same speed but with redundancy', 'Requires 4 disks minimum', 1, 'medium', '2026-05-23 16:25:36'),
