(406, 'Troubleshooting', 'A user cannot print to a shared network printer. Others can print. What is the FIRST thing to check?', 'The printer itself', 'The user\'s computer — default printer settings or print spooler', 'The network switch', 'The printer driver on the server', 1, 'medium', '2026-05-23 17:18:35'),
