(409, 'Troubleshooting', 'A user reports that their mouse double-clicks when they single-click. What is the solution?', 'Replace the mouse', 'Adjust the double-click speed in mouse settings, or replace the mouse if hardware issue', 'Reinstall Windows', 'Update the graphics driver', 1, 'easy', '2026-05-23 17:18:35'),
(410, 'Troubleshooting', 'A technician hears a continuous beep from a computer that just had RAM replaced. What is the MOST likely cause?', 'Incompatible or improperly seated RAM', 'Power supply failure', 'Hard drive failure', 'CPU overheating', 0, 'easy', '2026-05-23 17:18:35'),
(411, 'Troubleshooting', 'A computer shows \"No Boot Device Found\". What should be checked FIRST?', 'The monitor', 'Boot order in BIOS and hard drive connections', 'The RAM modules', 'The power supply', 1, 'easy', '2026-05-23 17:18:35'),
(412, 'Troubleshooting', 'A user reports that their keyboard types numbers instead of letters on some keys. What is the likely cause?', 'Keyboard hardware failure', 'Num Lock is on and they are using the embedded numeric keypad on a laptop', 'Virus infection', 'Driver corruption', 1, 'easy', '2026-05-23 17:18:35'),
(413, 'Troubleshooting', 'A projector lamp has been used for 2500 hours and the image is dim. What should be done?', 'Increase brightness in settings', 'Replace the projector lamp', 'Clean the lens', 'Replace the projector', 1, 'easy', '2026-05-23 17:18:35'),
