(416, 'Troubleshooting', 'A computer fan is very loud and the computer shuts down after 10 minutes of use. What is the problem?', 'Power supply failing', 'CPU overheating due to dust or fan failure', 'RAM failure', 'Hard drive failing', 1, 'easy', '2026-05-23 17:18:35'),
(417, 'Troubleshooting', 'A laptop screen is cracked. What is the proper repair procedure?', 'Replace the entire laptop', 'Replace the LCD screen assembly following manufacturer guidelines', 'Use software to fix it', 'Apply tape over the crack', 1, 'medium', '2026-05-23 17:18:35'),
(418, 'Troubleshooting', 'A user reports that their computer date and time reset every morning. What is the cause?', 'Faulty CMOS battery on the motherboard', 'Windows update issue', 'User error', 'Network time sync problem', 0, 'easy', '2026-05-23 17:18:35'),
(419, 'Troubleshooting', 'A technician installs a new graphics card but gets no display. The onboard graphics work. What should be checked?', 'The monitor', 'BIOS settings to ensure discrete GPU is enabled and power connectors are attached', 'The hard drive', 'The RAM', 1, 'hard', '2026-05-23 17:18:35'),
(420, 'Troubleshooting', 'A user reports that USB devices work intermittently. What is a common cause?', 'Outdated or corrupted USB drivers or power management settings', 'Faulty RAM', 'CPU overheating', 'Monitor failure', 0, 'medium', '2026-05-23 17:18:35'),
(421, 'Networking', 'What is the purpose of a network switch?', 'To connect multiple devices on the same network and forward data based on MAC addresses', 'To connect different networks together', 'To assign IP addresses', 'To secure the network', 0, 'easy', '2026-05-23 17:18:35'),
